strings:
<voice_0x01000D99><se_high>Red: You just keep turnin' up like a bad penny,
don't ya!? Wot the 'ell d'ya want this time, eh?
<voice_0x01000D9A><se_low>Yangus: ...I was just thinkin' ya might be lonely, is all. Thought I'd drop in an' see 'ow ya was.
<voice_0x01000D9B><se_high>Red: You tryin' to chat me up or somefin'!?

<voice_0x01000D9C><se_high>Red: I've 'ad it up to 'ere wiv your rubbish!
Get out of 'ere! Sort yerself out!
